WEBVTT

00:00:27.137 --> 00:00:30.071
"But Coach, those people
are really important and smart."

00:00:30.095 --> 00:00:32.172
(Laughter)

00:00:32.196 --> 00:00:33.518
"I know that."

00:00:34.793 --> 00:00:38.510
"But Coach, why are you speaking?
You hate public speaking."

00:00:39.071 --> 00:00:40.580
"I do," I admitted,

00:00:42.334 --> 00:00:45.933
"But it's important that I speak about us,
that I speak about your journeys,

00:00:45.957 --> 00:00:47.116
about my journey.

00:00:47.140 --> 00:00:48.409
People need to know."

00:00:49.098 --> 00:00:51.811
The students at the all-refugee
school that I founded

00:00:51.835 --> 00:00:54.227
decided to end with some
words of encouragement.

00:00:54.251 --> 00:00:56.070
"Cool! It better be good, Coach."

00:00:56.094 --> 00:00:58.794
(Laughter)

00:00:58.818 --> 00:01:02.376
There are 65.3 million people
who have been forcibly displaced